        <del class="strickenText">the organization, operation, powers, regulations, and management of state departments, agencies, institutions, and advisory committees;</del>
      </div>
      <div class="textpara" style="text-indent:4em;line-height:120%;text-align:justify;padding-left:0em;padding-right:0em">[<del class="strickenText">(2)</del>
