        <del class="strickenText">&nbsp;</del>
        <del class="strickenText">&nbsp;</del>
        <del class="strickenText">advances in science and technology, including telecommunications, electronic technology, or automated data processing, by state agencies, including institutions of higher education;</del>
      </div>
